use-package fields:

  :ensure      install package automatically if needed.
  :init        code executed before package load.
  :config      code executed after package load.
  :mode        files triggering this package.
  :interpreter interpreters triggering this package.

https://github.com/jwiegley/use-package

--

if use-package freaks out about not finding a package on emacs start-up, do M-x
package-refresh-contents, exit emacs and try again.
